query:
INSERT INTO tokens (index, token_address, contract_index, contract_sub_index, metadata_url, token_id, init_transaction_index)
                    VALUES ((SELECT COALESCE(MAX(index) + 1, 0) FROM tokens), $1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
                    ON CONFLICT (token_address)
                    DO UPDATE SET metadata_url = EXCLUDED.metadata_url
